metadata.name: those rainy days #40
metadata.description:
endless loop.

instructions:

press 'r' to start and stop rain sound ( works in fullscreen mode ).
tap anywhere to freeze and unfreeze animations.
mouse interacts with camera perspective.

note: all shapes are generative and code based. there are a couple image textures that I created  for this piece, to "dirty" certain elements, but there are no pre-created objects, shapes or layouts. It is all generated when minting.
 
please be patient as it takes a few seconds to load. thank you for your understanding.

metadata.name: Negative Space #74
metadata.description:
In this piece, special attention is paid to negative space, which is emphasized by simple / bold color palettes.

6 different styles
- Network
- Parachutes
- Flow
- Limbs
- Arcs
- Florals

9 different color palettes
- dark
- light
- yellow
- blue
- red
- green
- blue and yellow
- red and blue
- multi

Press any key to download a hi-res png.

p5.js script with a custom shader. Depending on the settings, it take some time to fully render / draw.

metadata.name: Weavemaker Mega #23
metadata.description:
Multiple full size weaves formulated by between 2 to 5 uniquely located walkers over 1250 frames.
Satisfying to watch the reveal, some palettes take a little longer than others to start to reveal.
Rarity includes:
- One of twenty palettes each with 5% rarity, although some may turn out rarer than others.
- Number of Walkers (2 to 5)
- Location of each Walker

Made by P1xelboy :
@p1x3lboy Mar 2022
